---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import { images } from "../assets/images";
---

<section class="emerge" id="emerge" aria-label="About the barrio">
	<div class="emerge-layout">
		<figure class="emerge-figure">
			<Image src={images.night2.src} alt={images.night2.alt} width={1200} class="emerge-photo" />
		</figure>

		<div class="emerge-text">
			<h2 class="emerge-heading">A chill-room<br />in the desert</h2>
			<p>
				Since 2013, we've harboured a web of wonderful wanderers that work hard, play hard, and take care of each other
				in the heat.
			</p>
			<p>
				We combine a chill atmosphere with a touch of nerdy craziness. Hammocks, paradoxes, surrealism, fuckery, and one
				of the best views on the playa.
			</p>
			<p class="emerge-kicker">Come to gather.<br />Stay to wonder.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.emerge {
		background: oklch(0.09 0.015 10);
		padding: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 8rem) clamp(1.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
	}

	.emerge-layout {
		max-width: 1360px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		gap: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
	}

	@media (min-width: 860px) {
		.emerge-layout {
			grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
			align-items: end;
		}
	}

	.emerge-figure {
		margin: 0;
		overflow: hidden;
		position: relative;
	}

	.emerge-figure::after {
		content: "";
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		pointer-events: none;
		background:
			linear-gradient(to right, oklch(0.09 0.015 10) 0%, transparent 18%),
			linear-gradient(to left, oklch(0.09 0.015 10) 0%, transparent 18%),
			linear-gradient(to bottom, oklch(0.09 0.015 10) 0%, transparent 18%),
			linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent 60%, oklch(0.09 0.015 10) 100%);
	}

	.emerge-photo {
		width: 100%;
		height: clamp(320px, 60vh, 680px);
		object-fit: cover;
		object-position: center center;
		display: block;
	}

	.emerge-text {
		max-width: 54ch;
	}

	.emerge-heading {
		font-family: "Bungee", sans-serif;
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
		color: oklch(0.96 0.008 80);
		line-height: 1.05;
		margin: 0 0 clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 2rem);
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}

	.emerge-text p {
		font-family: "Jost", sans-serif;
		font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1.5vw, 1.05rem);
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: oklch(0.72 0.01 80);
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
		max-width: 54ch;
	}

	.emerge-kicker {
		font-family: "Bungee", sans-serif;
		font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
		color: oklch(0.82 0.2 322) !important;
		line-height: 1.4;
		margin-top: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem) !important;
		text-shadow:
			0 0 6px oklch(0.62 0.26 322 / 0.7),
			0 0 18px oklch(0.62 0.26 322 / 0.4),
			0 0 40px oklch(0.62 0.26 322 / 0.2);
	}
</style>
